随心所欲地结束战争。美国和以色列必为其所作所为表示悔恨，不得再威胁西亚地区的任何国家，让各国根据本国人民的意愿做出决定，以免此类局面再次发生。战争不会停止，我们的领导人、人民和军队向死敌复仇的意志比以往任何时候都更加坚定。敌人不要妄想通过心理战和散布谎言动摇伊朗国家和军队的意志。」 伊朗提出停火条件"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-02ee91ea6aa60853c67c822378a1dc3a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "101 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2014694863774377798"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIw9/d3JaSlephEAMaCTExODcwMDUyMSCu2b7NBjAAOIsHQBJyEzIwMTQ2OTQ4NjM3NzQzNzc3OTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1773204249.849954", "card_id": "Q_2012606421498352481", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "今年的政府工作报告到底说了啥？有哪些我们普通人应该关注的信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0c79c62b7028a30076a8aae56cd469d2.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "101 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2012606421498352481"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIw9/d3JaSlephEAMaCTExODYzMjYyMSCrp6DNBjAAOMEBQBNyEzIwMTI2MDY0MjE0OTgzNTI0ODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1773204249.850377", "card_id": "Q_2012457177646925187", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么要比方程式赛车，无限制赛车不刺激么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f12ab23f25f1631cdbd84bdb882ec62_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "100 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2012457177646925187"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIw9/d3JaSlephE