是预制菜，给消费者选择权。孙宝国建议，餐馆应明确告诉消费者是否使用预制菜，不应存在信息不对称的情况。 委员建议：餐馆应标明预制菜，让顾客自己选"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-07491e47b0b1da0afbbe7434d642cc5b_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2014671725665736119"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIw9/d3JaSlephEAMaCTExODY5OTQ4MyCirr7NBjAAOI8BQBtyEzIwMTQ2NzE3MjU2NjU3MzYxMTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1773204249.854210", "card_id": "Q_2002843647255803271", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "洗衣机除菌技术成熟了吗？为什么「分区洗衣机」和「内衣洗衣机」反而更火了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2fdbf055544581eedc23dd6cd9257bd9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2002843647255803271"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIw9/d3JaSlephEAMaCTExODMzNjM5NCDgnpLMBjAAOCNAHHITMjAwMjg0MzY0NzI1NTgwMzI3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1773204249.854512", "card_id": "Q_47264301", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在数学或是计算机科学中，有什么优美的结论会有一些小的特例不满足？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "以前看到过某问题的一个优美的结论，但是这个结论在 n=5 还是 6 的时候是不对的。 于是来请教知乎的大神们还有哪些这样的例子。 UPD: 感觉有些回答偏离了我的意思。 我找了很久总算找到了以前看到的那个问题「求一个 N 个节点的 AVL 叶子节点最大深度差」。 如果计算「最大深度差为 X 的最小的 N」，那么随着 X=0,1,2,3,4…N=1,4,12,33... 而且十分优美地是：这个数列通项正好是 Fib[2*n]-1 ！ 可惜的是，N=6 的时候不满足以上的结论。理论上此时 AVL 最大深度差是 1，但是其实是 0！ UPD2: 题主在写这个问题的时候，其实还期望反例不要是最小的几个值。如果在一个结论在「中间」的一个地方有特例，而对于「两侧」都是成立的，感觉更加的神奇。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/47264301"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iw9/d3JaSlephEAMaCDExMTIwMDYyIP3q5LoFMAA46AVAHXIINDcyNjQzMDF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}]}